{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2019-08-29-BEM/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"박준우 블로그"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"b356963d-8da3-53b1-bed3-d8955b487edb","excerpt":"- BEM이란? BEM은 CSS Architecture의 하나입니다. Block Element Modifier의 줄임말입니다. ex) header__form—email Block(전체를 감싸고 있는 블럭요소) 독립적으로 의미가 있는 컴포넌트를 의미합니다. header, footer…","html":"<h2>- BEM이란?</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>BEM은 CSS Architecture의 하나입니다.</li>\n<li>Block Element Modifier의 줄임말입니다.</li>\n<li>ex) header__form—email</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Block(전체를 감싸고 있는 블럭요소)</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>독립적으로 의미가 있는 컴포넌트를 의미합니다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>block<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>...<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>header, footer, nav, main등의 컨텐츠 영역을 block으로 간주할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 550px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/669755db10a133e2ede9cf1470a77258/d7854/css_architecture1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.31645569620254%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"bem1\"\n        title=\"bem1\"\n        src=\"/static/669755db10a133e2ede9cf1470a77258/d7854/css_architecture1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/669755db10a133e2ede9cf1470a77258/ff44c/css_architecture1.jpg 158w,\n/static/669755db10a133e2ede9cf1470a77258/a6688/css_architecture1.jpg 315w,\n/static/669755db10a133e2ede9cf1470a77258/d7854/css_architecture1.jpg 550w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>더 구체적으로, header block은 logo block, search form block, authorization block을 포함할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/149b012a4cacff1b49676ca3037a6dde/20c85/css_architecture3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 49.36708860759494%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"bem2\"\n        title=\"bem2\"\n        src=\"/static/149b012a4cacff1b49676ca3037a6dde/f058b/css_architecture3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/149b012a4cacff1b49676ca3037a6dde/c26ae/css_architecture3.png 158w,\n/static/149b012a4cacff1b49676ca3037a6dde/6bdcf/css_architecture3.png 315w,\n/static/149b012a4cacff1b49676ca3037a6dde/f058b/css_architecture3.png 630w,\n/static/149b012a4cacff1b49676ca3037a6dde/40601/css_architecture3.png 945w,\n/static/149b012a4cacff1b49676ca3037a6dde/20c85/css_architecture3.png 999w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</li>\n<li>block은 클래스의 어근을 형성하고, 항상 맨 앞에 위치합니다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Element</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>독립적으로는 의미가 없으며 Block에 붙어서 사용되는 컴포넌트를 의미합니다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>block<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>block__element<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>...<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>element는 block이 포함하고 있는 한 조각입니다.</li>\n<li>예를 들어 위에서 보았던 block이미지에서, menu item은 menu block 바깥에서는 사용될 수 없습니다.\n따라서 각각의 메뉴아이템은 element입니다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 513px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e0ea3b9749e96d5c305f8f546708dbd4/267f6/css_architecture4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 59.49367088607595%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"bem3\"\n        title=\"bem3\"\n        src=\"/static/e0ea3b9749e96d5c305f8f546708dbd4/267f6/css_architecture4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e0ea3b9749e96d5c305f8f546708dbd4/c26ae/css_architecture4.png 158w,\n/static/e0ea3b9749e96d5c305f8f546708dbd4/6bdcf/css_architecture4.png 315w,\n/static/e0ea3b9749e96d5c305f8f546708dbd4/267f6/css_architecture4.png 513w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 513px) 100vw, 513px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>두개의 underscore로 연결하여 블럭 다음에 위치시킵니다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.block__element</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> none<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.header__logo</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">property</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> value<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.header__tagline</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">property</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> value<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.header__navigation</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">property</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> value<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>Modifiers</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>modifier는 block 또는 element의 속성입니다.</p>\n<p>이 속성은 block이나 element의 외관이나 상태를 변화시킵니다.</p>\n<p>기본적으로, class명은 반복하여 재사용할 수 있게 하기위해 존재합니다.</p>\n<p>특정 요소의 스타일을 수정해야할 필요가 있을때 modifier를 활용하게 됩니다.</p>\n<p>이때, element나 block다음에 두개의 하이픈’—‘을 추가하여 modifier를 표시합니다.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.block__element--modifier</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> none<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>다음처럼 focused된 tab3를 modifiers라고 볼 수 있습니다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/05ef20c0af4b79cb4f52f1c8d1cd73dd/59822/css_architecture5.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 62.65822784810127%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"bem4\"\n        title=\"bem4\"\n        src=\"/static/05ef20c0af4b79cb4f52f1c8d1cd73dd/f058b/css_architecture5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/05ef20c0af4b79cb4f52f1c8d1cd73dd/c26ae/css_architecture5.png 158w,\n/static/05ef20c0af4b79cb4f52f1c8d1cd73dd/6bdcf/css_architecture5.png 315w,\n/static/05ef20c0af4b79cb4f52f1c8d1cd73dd/f058b/css_architecture5.png 630w,\n/static/05ef20c0af4b79cb4f52f1c8d1cd73dd/59822/css_architecture5.png 916w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>사용 예</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>다음과 같은 버튼을 만든다고 하면,</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 361px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/bfa04d72072fccdd9bb74a0c31faa70a/e5d82/css_architecture2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 10.126582278481013%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"bem5\"\n        title=\"bem5\"\n        src=\"/static/bfa04d72072fccdd9bb74a0c31faa70a/e5d82/css_architecture2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/bfa04d72072fccdd9bb74a0c31faa70a/ff44c/css_architecture2.jpg 158w,\n/static/bfa04d72072fccdd9bb74a0c31faa70a/a6688/css_architecture2.jpg 315w,\n/static/bfa04d72072fccdd9bb74a0c31faa70a/e5d82/css_architecture2.jpg 361w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 361px) 100vw, 361px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>button<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Normal button<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>button button--state-success<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Success button<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>button button--state-danger<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Danger button<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.button</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> inline-block<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border-radius</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 3px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 7px 12px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1px solid #d5d5d5<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-image</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">linear-gradient</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>#eee<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> #ddd<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 700 13px/18px Helvetica<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> arial<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.button--state-success</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #fff<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #569e3d <span class=\"token function\">linear-gradient</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>#79d858<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> #569e3d<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> repeat-x<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.button--state-danger</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #900<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>공부, 그림 출처</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://getbem.com/faq/\">http://getbem.com/faq/</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.theodo.com/2015/10/how-i-stopped-worrying-and-learned-to-love-the-css-with-bem/\">https://blog.theodo.com/2015/10/how-i-stopped-worrying-and-learned-to-love-the-css-with-bem/</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://en.bem.info/methodology/key-concepts/\">https://en.bem.info/methodology/key-concepts/</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://webclub.tistory.com/263\">https://webclub.tistory.com/263</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.naver.com/PostView.nhn?blogId=dilrong&#x26;logNo=221496133579\">https://blog.naver.com/PostView.nhn?blogId=dilrong&#x26;logNo=221496133579</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"BEM이란?","date":"August 29, 2019","description":"BEM이란 뭘까?"}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2019-08-08-vscode-tips/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Visual Studio Code Tips"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2019-09-01-git-upstream/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"fork한 저장소를 최신 원본과 동기화시키기"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"b356963d-8da3-53b1-bed3-d8955b487edb","previousPostId":"1a0bee91-0248-5884-881b-09155192987f","nextPostId":"e5f8e6aa-3eca-5219-9cbb-52977306855e"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","916993862"]}